A middle-aged scientist has gone to great lengths to impress a girl - but unfortunately for him his chat up technique just did cut it.

Wu Lei, 54, from Taiwan, was so keen on 23-year-old Ling Lin he went to the hairdresser and asked for a short back and sides that would help him stand out.

And he got it when his hair was styled into a perfectly right-angled flat top - a bit like a Lego man. With that, he thought he could corner her.

